{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0003", "text": "兜個圈 有拖拍兼有錢", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 9}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 4, 3, 5, 3, 4, 3, 5, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["dau1", "go3", "hyun1", "jau5", "to1", "paak3", "gim1", "jau5", "cin4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "兜個", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "圈", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "拖", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "拍", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "兼有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "錢", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "幸災樂禍", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2140", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0004", "text": "如果你走先 下個月轉運怎算", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 9, 5, 9, 3, 2, 4, 2, 9, 2, 9, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jyu4", "gwo2", "nei5", "zau2", "sin1", "haa6", "go3", "jyut6", "zyun2", "wan6", "zam2", "syun3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "如果", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "走", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "先", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "下個月", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "轉運", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怎算", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "幸災樂禍", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2140", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0005", "text": "沉溺到底 還擊到底", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 8}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 3, 4, 9, 0, 3, 4, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["cam4", "nik1", "dou3", "dai2", "waan4", "gik1", "dou3", "dai2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "沉溺", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "到底", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "還擊", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "到底", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "幸災樂禍", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2140", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0006", "text": "你先會得到這抗體 先會一世不再感染", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 3, 3, 4, 5, 4, 9, 3, 3, 4, 3, 4, 9, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["nei5", "sin1", "dak1", "dou3", "ze5", "kong3", "tai2", "sin1", "jat1", "sai3", "bat1", "zoi3", "gam2", "jim5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "先會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "得到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "抗體", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "先", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一世", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不再", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "感染", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "幸災樂禍", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2140", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0007", "text": "所以 人不會好一世", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 8}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [9, 5, 0, 3, 9, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["so2", "ji5", "jan4", "bat1", "hou2", "jat1", "sai3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "所以", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "好", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一世", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "幸災樂禍", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2140", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0008", "text": "不會衰一世 先玩之不厭", "structure": {"line_index": 8, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 3, 3, 4, 3, 9, 3, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["bat1", "seoi1", "jat1", "sai3", "sin1", "waan2", "zi1", "bat1", "jim3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "不會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "衰", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一世", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "先玩", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "之", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不厭", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "幸災樂禍", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2140", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0007", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0009", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0009", "text": "淡市沒有反應 繼續再打拼", "structure": {"line_index": 9, "char_count": 11}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 5, 2, 5, 9, 4, 2, 4, 9, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["daam6", "si5", "mut6", "jau5", "faan2", "gai3", "zuk6", "zoi3", "daa2", "ping1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "淡市", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "反應", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "繼續", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "再", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "打拼", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "幸災樂禍", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2140", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0008", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0010", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0010", "text": "疫症沒有反應 就轉換血清 絕嶺上求勝", "structure": {"line_index": 10, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 4, 2, 5, 9, 2, 9, 2, 4, 3, 2, 5, 0, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jik6", "zing3", "mut6", "jau5", "faan2", "zau6", "zyun2", "wun6", "hyut3", "cing1", "zyut6", "ling5", "kau4", "sing3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "疫症", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "反應", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "就", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "轉換", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "血清", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "絕", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "嶺上", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "求勝", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "幸災樂禍", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2140", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0009", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0011", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0011", "text": "今年多災星 險境 當走火警 訓練你反應", "structure": {"line_index": 11, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 0, 3, 3, 3, 9, 9, 9, 9, 9, 4, 2, 5, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["gam1", "nin4", "do1", "zoi1", "sing1", "him2", "ging2", "zau2", "fo2", "ging2", "fan3", "lin6", "nei5", "faan2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "今年", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "多", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "災星", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "險境", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "當走", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "火警", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "訓練", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "反應", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "幸災樂禍", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2140", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0010", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0012", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0012", "text": "受難應該也高興(索氣勝過有絕症)", "structure": {"line_index": 12, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 0, 3, 5, 3, 3, 4, 4, 4, 5, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["sau6", "naan4", "goi1", "jaa5", "gou1", "hing1", "hei3", "sing3", "gwo3", "jau5", "zyut6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "受難", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "應該", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "高興", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "(", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "索氣", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "勝過", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "絕症", "pos": "X"}, {"text": ")", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "幸災樂禍", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2140", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0011", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0013", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0013", "text": "損失都不輕 反省 你應不應 撥亂再反正", "structure": {"line_index": 13, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [9, 3, 3, 3, 3, 9, 9, 5, 3, 2, 2, 4, 9, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["syun2", "sat1", "dou1", "bat1", "hing1", "faan2", "saang2", "nei5", "bat1", "but6", "lyun6", "zoi3", "faan2", "zing3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "損失", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "都", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不輕", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "反省", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "應不應", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "撥亂", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "再", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "反正", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "幸災樂禍", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2140", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0012", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjE0MA_0014", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
